org.bukkit.event.Cancellable
public final class BlockAccessMenuEvent extends org.bukkit.event.block.BlockEvent implements org.bukkit.event.Cancellable
Called when a player is trying to access a blocks lock menu. Can be cancelled to prevent the inventory from opening up.
Since:
1.0.0
